<p><span class="vocab">先生<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>先生</rb><rt>せんせい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Sensei (elder one; teacher - used here as form of address)</span></span>のいう<span class="vocab">事<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>事</rb><rt>こと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;matters</span></span>は、ここで<span class="vocab">切れる<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>切</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>れる&nbsp;run out; come to an end</span></span><span class="vocab">様子<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>様子</rb><rt>ようす</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sign; appearance</span></span>もなかった。<span class="vocab">私<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>私</rb><rt>わたくし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;I; me</span></span>はまたここで<span class="vocab">何か<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何</rb><rt>なに</rt></ruby>か&nbsp;something</span></span>いおうとした。すると<span class="vocab">後ろ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>後</rb><rt>うし</rt></ruby>ろ&nbsp;behind; in back</span></span>の<span class="vocab">方<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>方</rb><rt>ほう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;direction</span></span>で<span class="vocab">犬<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>犬</rb><rt>いぬ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;dog</span></span>が急に<span class="vocab">吠え出した<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>吠</rb><rt>ほ</rt></ruby>え<ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>だ</rt></ruby>した&nbsp;began to bark</span></span>。先生も私も<span class="vocab">驚いて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>驚</rb><rt>おどろ</rt></ruby>いて&nbsp;in surprise</span></span>後ろを<span class="vocab">振り返った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>振</rb><rt>ふ</rt></ruby>り<ruby><rb>返</rb><rt>かえ</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;turned around; looked back</span></span>。</p>

