<p>奥さんは<span class="vocab">笑いながら<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>笑</rb><rt>わら</rt></ruby>いながら&nbsp;smiling; laughing</span></span>先生の<span class="vocab">顔<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>顔</rb><rt>かお</rt></ruby>&nbsp;face</span></span>を<span class="vocab">見た<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>た&nbsp;looked at</span></span>。</p>

